Therefore, by conducting the reference measurements, the relative values Vr%, Vt% and Vct% can be calculated as:12Vr%=Vr−Vr,0Vref−Vref,0;Vt%=Vt−Vt,0Vref−Vref,0;Vct%=Vct-Vct,0Vref-Vref,0.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
